videos.description: Villanova freshman Saddiq Bey has his first 3-pointer bounce around the rim and fall and his second attempt from deep banks home.
videos.headline: Bey gets lucky on back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Villanova's highly touted freshman Jahvon Quinerly shows off the range and drains the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Jahvon Quinerly knocks down 3

videos.description: Villanova big man Eric Paschall steps behind the line and knocks down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Paschall puts in the 3

videos.description: Villanova's Phil Booth knocks down the three with under a minute to go in the first half.
videos.headline: Booth comes off screen and drains 3
